Open Call In Person Auditions Mon. & Tues. Nov 10 & 11 at 7pm for The 39 Steps by Patrick Barlow, Directed by Liz Bove. Performances: Jan. 9-18: Fri. & Sat. 8pm & Sundays 2pm + 2pm Matinee Sat. 1/17. More Details @ [https://www.facebook.com/share/17ZdspnYwH/](https://www.facebook.com/share/17ZdspnYwH/) Auditions @HeightsPlayers 26 Willow Place Brooklyn, NY 11201. (718) 237-2752. Please bring a headshot and resume, sides available on website. Please be sure to be available for in person call backs. NO pay.

CHARACTER BREAKDOWN:

**A familiarity with the Hitchcock film, The 39 Steps (1935), is highly recommended as the play is a direct spoof on the film. You may find this on ****[Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jfVtoPN3BVk)****.**
**Richard Hannay:** 30s-40s. A Hitchcock-esque suave, dashing, debonaire fellow. A physically adept comedian. Must be able to do a British accent. 

**Annabella Schmidt:** 20s-30s. An exotic and intriguing spy. Must be able to do a German accent. Actress will also play Margaret. 

**Pamela**: 20s-30s. The quintessential Hitchcock-esqe leading lady. She is bold, emotionally and intellectually intelligent. British accent required. 

**Margaret**: 20s-30s. The wife of a stern religious Scottish farmer. Scottish accent required. Actress will also play Annabella. 

**Clown #1 **& **Clown #2:** Any age, gender, race. Vivacious and debonair, both clowns expertly execute multiple male and female roles with skillful physical comedic skills.  English and Scottish accents a must.

‚ÄúStep into the shadows for an unforgettable night of darkly dazzling musical theater. This brand-new cabaret dives into the thrilling worlds of Lizzie: The Rock Musical, The Addams Family, Bat Boy: The Musical, and Sweeney Todd. Featuring a killer cast of powerhouse voices, the evening will blend rock energy, wicked humor, and hauntingly beautiful melodies in a celebration of the darker side of Broadway. Conceived and directed by Gabrielle Dillinger, this electrifying concert invites audiences to embrace the strange, the spooky, and the spectacular. Come experience a night that‚Äôs deliciously twisted and devilishly fun.‚Äù

All auditions due November 27th @11:59PM, with us getting in touch on November 30th.

Audition Call
The Old Kip on Meatham Estate

We are seeking three performers who self identify as women. We welcome performers from all backgrounds, abilities, body types, and training pathways. Curiosity, openness, and a willingness to investigate new approaches are highly valued. An interest in exploring physicality and text is important. We are particularly interested in hearing from immigrants, and especially from performers from Brazil, although this opportunity is open to all. This audition is for a project taking place in February at Theatre Deli.

The audition will take place on 7 December for invited candidates only.
Time: 11:00 to 17:00.

To be considered, please send by 28.11.25:
‚Ä¢ Your CV
‚Ä¢ A short video of you performing any text of your choice. This can be filmed on a phone and should not be edited.

Send your materials to: producer@viniciussalles.co.uk

EMERGENCY CAST CALL! VOLUNTEER ONLY

Hello everyone, my name is Cian and I am a level 6 film student at the University of Staffordshire, putting together my final year project, Metalhead.

Until recently, I had an actor attached to play the role of a doctor in my film. That actor cannot find the time for my shoot dates any longer, so i put the question to you.

Can you fill the role of a doctor for my project? Can you play an overworked, stern authority figure who can give the protagonist bad news?

My shoot date is Monday 10th November, filming in Stoke-on-Trent from 11am-5pm. Please let me know if this works for you!

If you think you can do this, please get in touch at:

Cian4472@hotmail.co.uk 

Or 

07722 490116 

Happy to provide anyone with more project details.

PART 3 ‚Äì ‚ÄúEchoes of That Night‚Äù

The night didn‚Äôt end when she walked away.
Her footsteps faded, but her presence lingered ‚Äî like the scent of rain after a storm. The city carried her with it; in the flicker of streetlights, in the rhythm of distant traffic, even in the hum of passing voices.

I found myself standing still, watching the same corner she disappeared into.
Funny how a moment so short could echo so loud.

As I walked home, everything looked the same ‚Äî the streets, the signs, the faces. But something inside me had shifted, quietly. It wasn‚Äôt love. Not yet. It was the feeling of being seen after a long time of just existing.

Later, as I lay in bed, the city outside kept whispering.
And in that whisper, I could still hear her voice ‚Äî soft, uncertain, real.

Maybe that‚Äôs how stories begin.
Not with promises‚Ä¶ but with pauses that make you wish they lasted longer.

- Migo Palendrom write up

üéÑ Casting Call: Princess Isadora ‚Äì The North Pole Experience, Liverpool.üéÑ

We‚Äôre seeking to recast a female-identifying performer aged 18+ to play Princess Isadora, one of the North Pole‚Äôs most charming and magical residents.

The ideal performer will have strong, confident acting ability and a natural warmth on stage. A confident singer is a bonus but not essential. Princess Isadora is playful, kind, and full of festive spirit, someone who captures the wonder of Christmas for every guest she meets.

---

Requirements:

Availability: Must be available on all of the following dates:
22nd, 23rd, 29th, 30th November
6th, 7th, 13th, 14th, 20th, 21st, 22nd, 23rd, 24th December.

Any additional day of rehearsal will also be agreed with the successful applicant. 

Location: Liverpool, United Kingdom

Experience: Experience in entertainment or performance is a plus, but we also welcome enthusiastic newcomers with a passion for performing.

Personality: Must embody the spirit of Christmas and bring the character to life with warmth and confidence.

Pay:

Rehearsals paid hourly at the National Minimum Wage (NMW) for your age group.

Performance days paid at ¬£160 per day, depending on role and experience.

Lunch and refreshments provided on all performance days.

Cast members also receive complimentary tickets for our Friends & Family Day, plus staff discount in our on-site merchandise shop.

---

Application Details:
Please email casting@thenorthpoleexperience.co.uk with:

1. Full name and contact details (phone number, email address)

2. Role you‚Äôre interested in auditioning for

3. Relevant performance or entertainment experience (if applicable)

4. Confirmation of full availability for the listed dates

5. Recent headshot(s) and/or showreel

---

Help us bring the magic of Christmas to life at The North Pole Experience ‚Äî we can‚Äôt wait to make magic with you! ‚ú®

Casting Call: Singer-Songwriter for Music Video (Unpaid)

Production Title: Christmas Music video 
Production Company: Superstar TV Entertainment Inc.
Type: Music Video
Location: Colorado (exact location TBD)
Filming Dates: late November early December 2025
Compensation: Unpaid (Copy, Credit, and Meals Provided)

---

About the Project

Superstar TV Entertainment Inc. is producing a heartfelt, cinematic music video featuring a singer-songwriter whose performance captures raw emotion and authenticity. This project is designed to highlight both the artist and visual storytelling ‚Äî similar in tone to Lewis Capaldi, Adele, or Noah Kahan.

The final video will be professionally shot and released across Superstar TV platforms, YouTube, and social media for maximum exposure.

---

Roles

üé§ Lead Artist / Singer-Songwriter (Principal Role)

Gender: Open to all

Age Range: 18‚Äì35

Vocal Style: Pop, acoustic, R&B, soul, or indie-folk preferred

Description: Emotionally expressive performer with on-camera presence. Must be comfortable lip-syncing to playback or performing live vocals. Guitar or piano ability is a plus.

Requirements: Must be reliable, punctual, and open to creative collaboration.

---

Supporting Roles (If applicable)

Love Interest: Ages 20‚Äì35, expressive and able to convey emotional connection.

Extras: Audience members, friends, or background talent for performance scenes.

---

Compensation

Unpaid (Copy, Credit, and Meals Provided)

You‚Äôll receive:

A professional-quality music video for your reel

IMDB credit under Superstar TV Entertainment Inc.

Networking opportunity for future paid productions

---

Submission Instructions

Please submit the following to tyler.schachtceo@outlook.com with the subject line:
Christmas Music Video ‚Äì [Your Name]‚Äù

Include:

Headshot or clear photo

Short performance clip or demo reel (YouTube or social media link accepted)

Short bio or resume

Contact information (email + phone number)

OH NO SHIT der skal s√¶ttes nogle krydser i kalenderen nu!

Casting datoerne til den helt nye teaterforestilling ‚ÄòForvokset‚Äô er nu fundet og vi gl√¶der os vanvittigt meget! 

Datoerne for casting i Kolding er dermed d. 10. og 11. februar 2026 og d. 13. og 14. februar afholdes der casting i Helsing√∏r. 
Selve forestillingen spilles som en teaterturn√©, s√•ledes at vi spiller rundt p√• sj√¶lland. Vi h√•ber p√• at kunne f√• lov at spille flere steder, men som det ser ud nu er det Helsing√∏r vi starter i. 
Forestillingsperioden ligger i sommerferien 2026. 

Vi s√∏ger 6 skuespiller til kr√¶vende roller, samt 4 personer til ensemble. 
Forestillingen omhandler temaerne misbrug, arv og milj√∏, sorg og k√¶rlighed, og bygger p√• digte fra Janus Halds digtsamling ‚ÄòSkyggesider‚Äô.

Vi s√∏ger:
Lise (19-25 √•r) Denne rolle har stor mulighed/sansynlighed for at f√• tildelt en sang

Vivi (19-25 √•r)

Oskar (20-30 √•r)

Lise og Vivi som b√∏rn (10-15 √•r)

Oskar som barn (10-15 √•r)

Ensamble (19-30 √•r)

OBS. Er du under 18 bedes du medbringe for√¶ldre underskrift/tilladelse.

Er du ik bare mega interreseret?! 
S√• synes vi, at du skal sende en mail til oh.no.shit.kontakt@gmail.com med dit navn, din alder, et billede af dig selv, hvilken rolle du s√∏ger, samt hvor og hvorn√•r du √∏nsker at komme til casting, s√• sender vi til geng√¶ld alle de praktiske informationer din vej.
Skulle du v√¶re s√• uheldig ikke at have mulighed for at deltage fysisk nogle af casting dagene, S√Ö er der hj√¶lp at hente, for s√• kan du sende et selftape til samme mail inden d. 14. februar 2026. 

Hvis dette er tilf√¶ldet m√• du meget gerne sende en mail med de samme informationer som hvis du skulle tilmelde dig den fysiske casting, og s√• bare n√¶vne at du sender selftape- s√• har vi nemlig mulighed for at have styr p√• det hele. 

Deadline for alle tilmedlings-mails, b√•de dem der melder sig til den super hyggelige fysiske casting, og dem der melder sig til at sende selftapes, er d. 1. februar 2026.
Vi gl√¶der os mere end man ka forestille sig!!

**K√∏benhavns Film- og Fotoskole s√∏ger 2 kvindelige skuespillere i alderen 18-22 √•r. **

Vennerne Rebekka, Fiona, Johanne og Lea taler √•bent om sex: Rebekka er uerfaren, Fiona er eksperimenterende, Lea har en k√¶reste, og Johanne (Joe) er til piger. Til en gymnasiefest g√•r det op for Fiona, hvor udenfor Rebekka f√∏ler sig. Trods sine egne usikkerheder omkring k√¶rlighed og sex vil Fiona hj√¶lpe hende med at f√• sin f√∏rste gang, inden gymnasiet slutter. Sammen begiver de sig ud p√• en √¶rlig, men gr√¶nses√∏gende rejse. CHERRY er en √¶rlig og s√•rbar film om unge kvinder og sex ‚Äì om at f√∏le skam over at have det, og skam over ikke at have haft det.

*Karakterbeskrivelse*

**Rebekka** (Cherry / HK) ‚Äì 19 √•r.

S√∏d, charmerende og udadvendt, men usikker, n√•r det bliver intimt. Hun har aldrig haft sex og skammer sig over det, men vil gerne v√¶re som de andre. I jagten p√• sin f√∏rste gang indser hun, at det m√•ske slet ikke er det, hun har brug for.

**Fiona** ‚Äì 20 √•r.

Rapk√¶ftet, selvsikker, omsorgsfuld og loyal. Hun har mange fyre, men ingen bliver ‚Äì og hun forst√•r ikke hvorfor. Bag den cool facade l√¶nges hun efter noget √¶gte og misunder Rebekkas uskyld. Hun tror, hun skal hj√¶lpe Rebekka med sex, men m√• selv gent√¶nke sit forhold til det.

Skuespilleren skal v√¶re komfortabel med intimscener.

Optagelserne foreg√•r i K√∏benhavn i perioden 17/11-25/11. 

Lyder det som noget for dig? Send en mail til juliagormsen@hotmail.com, hvor du inkluderer showreel. 

I emnefeltet skriv gerne "CHERRY - rollens navn". 

De bedste hilsner

Holdet bag *CHERRYüçí*

*SHOW REEL OPPORTUNITY*

Hey everyone!! 

Looking for four people to fill spots in the Actors Saga Screen Intensive  Classes next week Tuesday 11th November for four weeks! 

It is run by Rich Lund who is an amazing Aussie acting coach and  actor himself. Through the  4 weeks we‚Äôll work on two different scenes that are filled and he also gives , as well as advice and a bit of direction on who to send them to and how to approach the conversation with agents or casting!

items.text:
**LAST MINUTE**

Would anyone be available for a Google Meet tonight at 7:30 as temporary fill-ins for a table read for those who can not attend? We would prefer to have different voices for all these different characters. This is for a recorded table read of our feature "INTERNAL DESCENT: A JEKYLL AND HYDE STORY" to send to one of our financial backers who will decide if this is the right project to finance. 

Please note that you will need to sign a Google Forms waiver to not release any information about the script, plot, characters, etc. to the public. and this may make you eligible for any future roles with us, or even additional roles to this project. We will also add you in the credits of this film, which we plan to go to festivals with. 

We need: 

3 men

4 women.

We will accept anyone but here is what the character descriptions are. I will not give character names yet. 

MEN: 

Character 1: (African American if possible)- A therapist who tries to help the main character extinguish his internal demons before they take over him completely; acts as a guide; maybe a little too emotionally invested; mentor; straight to the point; wise; firm but caring; (Think of Characters like Coach Ken Carter from "Coach Carter" or  Sean Maguire from "Good Will Hunting") 

Character 2: (Caucasian if Possible)- A loudmouthed Southern redneck who uses his engine and his intimidation tactics to humiliate and torment the main character; overcompensating; clearly a right-wing extremist

Character 3 (Caucasian if Possible)- A sidekick to the loudmouthed Southern redneck who uses his camera to try to intimidate; brash; unfiltered; also right-wing extremist

WOMEN:

Character 1: (Caucasian if Possible)- Unfiltered self-entitled head of household; dismisses mental illness as "being dramatic"; demeaning; bullying;

Character 2: (Caucasian if possible) Early 20's- Daughter of Character 1; bragging; boastful

Character 3: (Caucasian if possible) Early 20's- Daughter of Character 1; insulting; boastful

Character 4: (Hispanic w/ thick accent) Kind-hearted; caring; reassuring; natural  
 

Please comment or message or call 573-944-0636. (Calling is best) 

Thanks! 

-Kevin from KC BLAZE ENTERTAINMENT

BE PREPARED LUZON!  GRABEEE ANG LAKI NG SAKOp!

after Visayas this coming weekend Sunday to Monday
pray for the Philippines ùêÄ ùêåùêéùêçùêíùêìùêÑùêë ùêíùêìùêéùêëùêå ùêàùêí ùêÇùêéùêåùêàùêçùêÜ! üåÄ‚ö†Ô∏è #PrayForThePhilippines

Mabilis pang lumalakas at patuloy na lumalawak ang bagyong may international name na #FungWong at ngayo‚Äôy isa nang Severe Tropical Storm Category, ayon sa Japan Meteorological Agency (JMA).

Taglay na ngayon ng bagyo ang lakas ng hangin na umaabot sa 95 kph at may pagbugso ng hangin na umaabot na sa 130 kph. Kumikilos ang bagyo sa direksyong pa-kanluran sa bilis na 15 kph.

Inaasahang mabilis itong lalakas bilang TYPHOON Category bukas at inaasahang papasok na ng PAR bukas ng gabi o madaling araw ng Sabado at tatawaging #UwanPH.

Bagama‚Äôt patuloy na tinutumbok ng bagyo ang #Northern-#CentralLuzon area, napakalawak ng bagyo kaya inaasahang mararamdaman din ang bagsik nito maging sa #MetroManila, #CALABARZON, #BicolRegion, #MIMAROPA, at maging sa #Visayas.

Patuloy na pinaghahanda ang mga kababayan natin sa mga nabanggit na lugar na paghandaan na po ang paparating na malakas na bagyo. 

HUWAG PO NATING BALEWALAIN ANG MGA PAULIT-ULIT NA MGA BABALA UKOL SA BAGYO DAHIL MALAWAK PO ANG SAKOP NITO.

Manatiling mag-antabay sa mga susunod pang update hinggil sa paparating na bagyo.

PWS/PSU
#BantayBagyo #UwanPH #FungWong

audition requirements:
all roles in this production are volunteer, non-union. xoxo welcomes performers 18+ of all genders, ethnicities, and skill levels to audition.

what to prepare:
1. a 32-bar cut of an upbeat musical theatre song in the style of the show.

2. a 1-2 minute contemporary, comedic monologue - this must be memorized.

how to apply:
please email your headshot and resume to theatre@xoxotv.ca to be scheduled with an audition time, or to request a self-tape submission.

character breakdowns can be found in our ‚Äúaudition package‚Äù link in bio.

Tuesdays & Thursdays 6:00pm to 10:00pm

items.text:
üì∏ PAID - Model Call: Head Spa Photo & Video Project! üßñ‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è

NON-UNION

We're looking for a female model to be featured in promotional photos and videos for a head spa in Vancouver! Please do not private message me; submit your application via email at the bottom to be considered.

‚ú®Who We're Looking 

Gender: Female
Hair Colour: Brunette (must have naturally dark or dyed brown hair)
Ages: 25-45 (approximate, flexible for the right fit)
Look: Must be comfortable being filmed enjoying a head spa treatment (head spa service only). A naturally serene, elegant, and refreshed look is key.

üé•Project Details
Location: Vancouver

Date: Currently planning for the last week of November; the exact date will be confirmed in advance.

Duration: 2 hours max

Acting experience: beneficial, but not required; no dialogue in the video
Content: Photos and video to be used on the client‚Äôs website and social media (Facebook/Instagram).
Compensation: Complimentary spa services during filming + your hourly rate.

How to Apply

If you're interested and fit the criteria, please send us:
1. A brief video introduction about yourself and why you'd be a great fit.
2. Your hourly rate.
3. If you have acting experience, your demo reel or links to the latest acting projects
4. 3-5 recent, clear, non-filtered photos (at least one close-up and one full-body shot).
5. Your availability for the last two weeks of November, including days and times

üìß Email your submission to casting@wildlyvisual.com with the subject line "Vancouver Head Spa Model Call."

==============================

F√ºr einen Bewerbungsfilm an der DFFB, der sich mit dem Thema ‚ÄûSehnsucht‚Äú auseinandersetzt, wird ein Schauspieler gesucht.

 

Der Film ist im Wesentlichen eine Neuinterpretation eines ber√ºhmten DFFB-Kurzfilms aus dem Jahr 1968, in dem eine rote Fahne von mehreren Personen durch die Stra√üen West-Berlins getragen wird. In unserer Version tr√§gt eine einzelne, verkleidete Person nacheinander verschiedene Flaggen.

 

Geplant ist ein Drehtag bzw. ein halber Drehtag, voraussichtlich Mitte November.

 

Eine Mappe mit weiteren Informationen zu Ablauf, Drehort usw. steht bereits zur Verf√ºgung. Die Teilnahme ist ehrenamtlich, bietet aber die M√∂glichkeit, Seterfahrung bei einem spannenden und humorvollen Projekt zu sammeln.

 

Liebe Gr√º√üe,

Thibauld W

sharedPost.text:
Atomic Theatre Wheat Ridge CO, presents:

Reading With The Rabbits a two-part youth theatre program designed to nurture young performers and inspire a love of literacy in the community.

Part One: Tween & Teen Performers
We provide tween and teen actors with a platform to showcase their character work, voice acting, and stage presence in front of a live audience. Using picture books as the medium, performers present their own directorial vision of a story of their choosing. Each show features 4‚Äì5 different stories, ensemble songs, and theatre games.

In a world where teen actors are often limited by age, gender, physical type, or busy school and sports schedules, Reading with the Rabbits offers a flexible, creative space to experiment and play.

Upcoming Auditions

Date: December 10

Time: 6-8PM

Location: Wheat Ridge Grange 

Performances: Saturday December13 at 1:30 and 3:30 

Theme: Winter 
J√≥lab√≥kafl√≥√∞i√∞ (book flood)

Actors will be given a stipend for their time. 

Audition Prep: reserve an audition time slot by emailing atomictheatre@gmail.com 

Actors are expected  to come with a performance ready picture  book to entertain young children and their families. Be perpared to show the book during  your staged reading.  You are the director/ actor and MC. Show off your different characters, find games within the pages, incorporate music or movement, break the fourth wall and invite the audience into your imagination. 

We appreciate your creativity and attention to detail, and can‚Äôt wait to experience your theatrical offering.

Be prepared to learn a sing-along song, minor choreography, and an improv game that will be played with the ensemble during the performances

Part Two: Community Story Hours
These donation-based performances are free and open to the public. Each event features:

Storytime performances where new readers watch older kids bring books to life.

Photo opportunities

Themed crafts to make the experience extra engaging for families.

* Usually bunnies who demonstrate how to be good audience members with their listening ears.  Our December showcase will be around a bonfire at a local urban farm weather permitting. The goats and chickens will be standing in for the rabbits.

Howdy Denver film community! We‚Äôre Wasteland of Wonder, a boutique film production company based here in Denver, CO that focuses on community building through creative collaboration. We‚Äôre seeking an actor for a music video and would love to engage with some new, local talent. Email us at wastelandofwonder@gmail.com for information about auditions!

TITLE: ‚ÄúDon‚Äôt Think‚Äù 

GENRE: Gothic industrial music video 

SYNOPSIS: ‚ÄúDon‚Äôt Think‚Äù explores themes of control and alienation both societally and personally with evocative and surreal imagery.  Our protagonist, Ezra, is an audience member at a surrealist concert- who slowly loses themself in the music. In a B plot we see manufacturers, men in a unique blend of industrial and medical garb, grooming and preparing Ezra for some kind of operation.  

CHARACTER: Ezra, (20s), feels alienated and unable to connect with others.  Ezra‚Äôs arc in the video is one of surrender and vulnerability, giving in to the pressures of everyone around them. 

This role is open casting for Men and Nonbinary actors of any race. Ideally the actor would be very skilled in physical work and have a dramatic background. 

PRODUCTION INFO

PRODUCTION COMPANY: Wasteland of Wonder (wastelandofwonder.com)

PRODUCTION TYPE: Music Video

CONTACT INFO: wastelandofwonder@gmail.com

COMPENSATION: The role will be compensated, rate TBD 

AUDITION INFORMATION: No audition, just send us a resume and reel :). Email us for further information. 

SHOOT SCHEDULE: Mid November 

FILMING LOCATION: Denver Metro & the Front Range

CASTING CALL: Protesters Voiceover ‚Äì ‚ÄúDenied Care‚Äù Series

Project Title: Denied Care
Production Company: Superstar TV Entertainment, Inc.
Type: Voiceover (Non-Union / Indie Production)
Location: Remote Recording Accepted
Compensation: paid 
Recording Date: November 15th

Looking for 3 voiceovers

---

PROJECT OVERVIEW

Denied Care is a scripted drama following Ava Winters, a young woman denied life-saving treatment by a broken healthcare system. The story exposes the real human cost of bureaucratic neglect through emotional, defiant, and darkly comedic storytelling.

Short Film feature a pivotal protest montage ‚Äî where voices from across the nation rise in solidarity. This casting call is for those protester voices ‚Äî raw, real, and unapologetic.

---

ROLE: PROTESTER VOICEOVER (MULTIPLE TALENTS)

Gender: Any
Age Range: 18‚Äì65
Accent: Open ‚Äî diverse voices encouraged
Tone: Authentic, passionate, emotional, and real
Vocal Quality:

Gritty, tired, but determined

Feels like you‚Äôve lived it ‚Äî not ‚Äúperformed‚Äù it

Think real activists, not voice actors

Examples of Lines (for audition):

‚ÄúWe are not invisible!‚Äù

‚ÄúYou can‚Äôt deny care to the living!‚Äù

‚ÄúWe‚Äôre sick, not silent!‚Äù

‚ÄúEvery denial has a name!‚Äù

‚ÄúWe are the denied ‚Äî and we‚Äôre not backing down!‚Äù

(Actors may be asked to record crowd-style chants, overlapping dialogue, and emotional reactions.)

---

RECORDING NOTES

Please record clean audio (WAV or MP3) with minimal background noise.

Multiple takes with varying energy levels are encouraged.

Shouting, chanting, and overlapping crowd energy welcome.

I en verden med et stigende tempo, t√•rnh√∏je f√∏devarepriser, krig i Europa og klimaangst f√•r vi - som vi er blevet tudet √∏rerne fulde af - f√¶rre b√∏rn end nogensinde. Mere pr√¶cist 1,5 barn i stedet for 2,01 barn pr. Kvinde. For at nuancere problematikken har vi brug for nogle modige medvirkende, som t√∏r lukke os ind i deres tvivl. Er det jer?

I kan h√∏re mange flere detaljer om formatet, hvis I skriver til mig p√• tlf. 50906007 eller nedenfor i kommentarsporet. Jeg vil gl√¶de mig til at tale med jer allesammen :)

Hej alle sammen!

Jeg kommer fra Danmark Radio, hvor vi her i Fakta- og Livsstilsafdelingen sidder og caster til et nyt TV-format. Vi leder efter par, som er i tvivl om, hvorvidt de skal have b√∏rn. 

I en verden med et stigende tempo, t√•rnh√∏je f√∏devarepriser, krig i Europa og klimaangst f√•r vi - som vi er blevet tudet √∏rerne fulde af - f√¶rre b√∏rn end nogensinde. Mere pr√¶cist 1,5 barn i stedet for 2,01 barn pr. Kvinde. For at nuancere problematikken har vi brug for nogle modige medvirkende, som t√∏r lukke os ind i deres tvivl. Er det jer?

I kan h√∏re mange flere detaljer om formatet, hvis I skriver til mig p√• tlf. 50906007 eller nedenfor i kommentarsporet. Jeg vil gl√¶de mig til at tale med jer allesammen :) 

De bedste hilsner

Clara Bruun, journalist, DR Aarhus

I kan h√∏re mange flere detaljer om formatet, hvis I skriver til mig p√• tlf. 50906007 eller nedenfor i kommentarsporet. Jeg vil gl√¶de mig til at tale med jer allesammen :) 

De bedste hilsner

Clara Bruun, journalist, DR Aarhus

**S√òGER DELTAGERE TIL DOKUMENTAR**

Vi er to filmskabere fra **Potemkin, den jyske filmskole**, der skal til at lave deres afgangsprojekt ‚Äî en smuk, poetisk mini-dokumentar med titlen *Med d√∏den p√• forkant*.

Filmen handler om, hvordan d√∏den kan komme f√∏r tiden ‚Äî og hvordan man lever videre, n√•r nogen forsvinder alt for tidligt. Vi √∏nsker at skabe et stille, √¶rligt og visuelt poetisk portr√¶t af k√¶rligheden og savnet, n√•r livet bliver afbrudt midt i det smukkeste.

For hvordan f√∏les det, n√•r d√∏den kommer p√• forkant?
N√•r man ikke bare savner en person, men ogs√• alt det, personen aldrig n√•ede at opleve?

Vi s√∏ger derfor tre personer, der har oplevet at miste **alt for tidligt**:
* en, der har mistet en **for√¶lder** i en ung alder
* en, der har mistet et **barn**
* og en, der har mistet sin **partner / √¶gtef√¶lle** f√∏r tiden

Optagelserne vil foreg√• i trygge rammer, og vi l√¶gger stor v√¶gt p√• respekt, n√¶rv√¶r og tillid i processen. Vi √∏nsker at skabe en film, der viser sorgen ‚Äì men ogs√• k√¶rligheden, styrken og de sm√• spor, der bliver tilbage.

Hvis du har lyst til at dele din historie ‚Äì eller bare vil h√∏re mere om projektet ‚Äì er du meget velkommen til at skrive til mig p√• denne mail: [sara774g@gmail.com](mailto:sara774g@gmail.com)

Vi h√•ber, at I vil v√¶re med til at skabe en smuk og n√¶rv√¶rende film!

De bedste hilsner, 

Sara Riahi (producer)
Freya Carlsen (instrukt√∏r)

Til workshoppen skal vi fordele os ud i forskellige roller; instrukt√∏r, fotograf, lydperson, klipper og skuespiller. 

Hver enkelt person skriver et dogme ned for deres rolle, f.eks; ‚ÄúSkuespilleren skal imitere J√∏rgen Leth‚Äù, ‚ÄúFotografen skal filme som en myre ser verden‚Äù eller ‚ÄúInstrukt√∏ren skal lave en historie om dengang kloakken ved den Permanente fl√∏d over i 1968‚Äù. 

Derefter blander vi det hele, tr√¶kker 5 tilf√¶ldige krav til hver film og g√•r i gang med at skabe filmen i vores grupper!

Om aftenen m√∏des vi og viser filmene til hinanden, samt alle der har lyst til at komme forbi og se dem.

Tilmelding og sp√∏rgsm√•l til siricwf@gmail.com

* Skriv hvilke roller du helst vil have under workshoppen:

Instrukt√∏r, fotograf, lydperson, klipper og skuespiller

* Hvilket udstyr du kan medbringe

Absolut alle er velkomne, erfaring med film eller ej!

items.text:
Hello everyone,

My name is Kayuran Moodley, and I am the founder of KM PICTURES, a newly established mobile film production based in Chatsworth, Durban. I‚Äôm currently in the process of expanding my team and looking for dedicated individuals to join me on this creative journey.

At this stage, I am specifically looking for:
üé• Camera Operator ‚Äì someone passionate about cinematography, able to work creatively with mobile or professional cameras, and interested in learning and experimenting with visual storytelling.
‚úÇÔ∏è Video Editor ‚Äì someone skilled in editing, sound design, and color grading, with a good eye for pacing, emotion, and storytelling (experience in horror or suspense genres will be an advantage).

KM PICTURES was started with a simple but powerful goal ‚Äî to create meaningful stories from small beginnings, using whatever tools and talent we have available. I believe in teamwork, creativity, and growth. This is a zero-budget project for now, but it‚Äôs built on passion, vision, and the goal of developing something great together from the ground up.

I‚Äôm currently working on my latest film script, and I want to collaborate with individuals who are serious about learning, growing, and being part of a local production that has the potential to expand into something bigger.

If you‚Äôre a filmmaker, editor, or someone who simply loves the art of storytelling and wants to build a future in film, I would love to connect with you. Let‚Äôs grow this production together and create something unique in the South African film space.

üìç Preferred Location: Chatsworth / Durban (for easier travel and teamwork)
üíº Production: Mobile Film (Independent / Zero Budget)
üìû Contact: 061 046 3076

Let‚Äôs bring creativity to life ‚Äî together.
‚Äî Kayuran Moodley
Founder & Director
KM PICTURES üé•

#KMPictures #FilmProduction #DurbanFilmmakers #IndependentFilm #CameraOperator #VideoEditor #Teamwork #FilmCrew #HorrorFilm #MobileFilmmaking #SouthAfricanCinema #PassionProject #CreativityInActio

items.text:
Hi everyone, I‚Äôm Chloe and I‚Äôm the producer of Snap Out Of It!, a UBC thesis sitcom short thriller written and directed by Sebastian Isaac-Gooden! We are currently searching for local Vancouver actors/non-actors for five roles played by one black lead actor, one black supporting actor, two white supporting actors and then one male actor of any ethnicity. See below for further character descriptions!

üìçVancouver, BC

üí∏Unpaid, with potential for pay based on experience/skills (meals & credit provided)

‚ú®Non-Union, but currently working to register under the UBCP ACTRA‚Äôs Student ULB Program

üéûÔ∏è Plans to premiere at the Persistence of Vision (POV) Film Festival run by UBC and hosted in the Rio Theatre next year

üì∏ Shoots from January 17th-19th, 2026

This film is a deeply personal exploration of the director‚Äôs experiences growing up Black in predominantly white communities and is set against the nostalgic, comforting, yet maddeningly repetitive backdrop of a sitcom world! It would truly mean the world to us if this project could play even a small part in creating more dynamic, well-written roles for Black actors in Vancouver!

So, if you are or know someone who might be interested in joining our team, please contact us at snapoutofit.film@gmail.com or @snapoutofit.film for self tape details and general inquiries

üìÖDEADLINE FOR SUBMISSIONS: Nov 21st, 2025

Tag a friend or a family member, spread the word, and we‚Äôre really excited to meet youüòä

Join us at our Demidov Studio London Festive Gathering on Friday December 19th at The Perseverance in London! üéâüéÑ‚òÉÔ∏è

As the year draws to a close, we invite you to join us for a drink and a toast to what has been a full and eventful year at the studio.

A moment to celebrate, reconnect and raise a glass to all the actors who have worked, explored, and created with us throughout the year, to the wider community of friends and collaborators who continue to inspire and support our work, and to new friends we haven‚Äôt yet met.

Everyone is warmly welcome. Come share some conversation and good cheer as we close out the year together and look forward to the next. 

Friday December 19th from 6pm - 11pm

In a private room upstairs at:

The Perseverance  36 Lamb‚Äôs Conduit Street, London WC1N 3NB

Please fill out this form via the link below üîó or drop us an email (office@demidovstudiolondon.com)  to let us know how many people to expect.

There is no entry fee.

Drinks will be available for purchase at this event. üç∑ 
Pizza will be provided! üçï 

https://www.demidovstudiolondon.com/events/festivegathering

Poster photos & design by üì∏: @kelsey_m_j

The International Conference "Performing Arts Between Tradition & Contemporaneity" was founded in 2003 to create a space for serious dialogue between traditional performance practices and contemporary artistic innovation. 

Over 22 editions, it has become a respected gathering point for performing arts professionals worldwide who refuse to see tradition and innovation as opposing forces, but rather as complementary elements in a living, evolving artistic practice.

Dates: December 18-22, 2025

Location: Schloss Laubegg, Austria

Capacity: Approximately 50 participants

Read More: https://www.nipai.org/post/22nd-performing-arts-conference  .

Schauspieler gesucht!

F√ºr ein Studentenprojektfilm suchen wir Freiwillige
die gerne Schauspielerisch vor die Kamera treten
wollen.
Aber erstmal: Wer sind wvir?
Wir sind eine Gruppe aus 4 Studenten des
Studiengangs "Film und Media Arts" der
Hochschule Flensburg.

Unser Ziel:
Als Pr√ºfungsleistung des Moduls "Kurzfilmprojekt
4" m√∂chten wir einen ca. 20 Min√ºtigen
Kom√∂dien-Kurzspielfilm drehen, der auch auf
Filmfestivals laufen soll.

Worum soll es im Film gehen?
Tobias , unser Hauptcharakter, befindet sich in
einer Misslichen Lage. Seitdem er einmal am Tag
seines Vorstellungsgespr√§ches verschlafen hat,
ger√§t er in eine Zeitschleife. In der durchlebt den
selben Tag immer und immer wieder. Und egal was
er auch tut, jedes Mal schafft er es nicht, p√ºnktlich
zum Vorstellungsgespr√§ch seiner Wunschfirma
zu kommen. Mit jeder Verbesserung alter Fehler
kommen neue Hinternisse hinzu.

F√ºr welche Rollen brauchen wir dich?

Zum einen:
m√§nnlich, 20-38 Jahre alt
f√ºr die Rolle des Tobias
(5-9 Drehtage)

Zum anderen:
weiblich, 50-70 Jahre alt
f√ºr die Rolle der Nachbarin
(1-2 Drehtage)

Und noch:
weiblich/m√§nnlich/divers, 20-50 Jahre alt
f√ºr die Rolle des/r Sekret√§r*in
(1 Drehtag)

Zum Dreh:
Drehen w√ºrden wir haupts√§chlich in Flensburg und
Umgebung, aber auch im Kreis-Eckernf√∂rde.
Wenn du also aus Schleswig-Holstein kommst,
w√§re das nat√ºrlich leichter.
Die Maximal 9 Drehtage finden irgendwann
zwischen der 2.Januarwoche und Ende Februar
2026 statt.
Den Zeitraum haben wir bewusst flexibler
gestellt, um sie mit den Terminen des
Hauptrollenschauspielers passender und leichter

planen zu k√∂nnen.
Catering ist nat√ºrlich inklusive
Hast du Interesse und keine Scheu vor der Kamera
zU spielen?

Schauspielerfahrungen (ob Profi oder Schultheater)
w√§ren sch√∂n, sind aber nicht zwingend notwendig.
Und reicht es wenn du mit Spass, Kreativit√§t und
Freude dabei bist.

Reiche deine Bewerbungen ein bei:

Email:mige7636@stud.hs-flensburg.de

oder schreib mich einfach √ºber diesen Account an

Wir freuen uns auf Dich!

topComments.text: Schade ,leider wohne ich in seesen. Ich bin ein Theater Kind, bin auf den brettern die die Welt bedeuten aufgewachsen da mein Onkel ein eigenes Theater in Bonn hatte ,Euro Theater  central ,habe ich alles dort gemacht ,auf der B√ºhne gestanden, Beleuchtung s technikerin gelernt ,als soufleuse gearbeitet ,ber√ºhmte Schauspieler kennen gelernt ,wie Heinz R√ºhmann, Gerd Fr√∂be ,Hannelore-knipper - m√∂sch, Angelika Kreyel usw
Eine tolle Herausforderung. Leider bin ich (noch)!kein ausgebildeter Schauspieler, allerdings schon sehr aktiv. Und leider wohne ich in K√∂ln.

En mand og en kvinde er de eneste to i publikum til singer/songwriter-koncert. Kvinden sidder, og ser lidt distanceret ud. Trist, nedtrykt. Manden l√¶gger m√¶rke til det, og ville √∏nske, han kunne g√∏re noget ved det. 

Til sidst rejser han sig, og danser (grimt). Viser s√•rbarhed for m√•ske at kunne distrahere kvinden.

Hun rejser sig op, og de danser sammen.

Der er ingen replikker, men det er en fordel, hvis man kan udtrykke sig via mimik.

**Honorar:**

Sybolsk honorar p√• 500 kr. pr. pers. gives som b-honorar. Plus vinyludgave af udgivelsen.

**Kontakt**:

Hvis du kan se dig selv i en af rollerne, s√• send et par vellignende fotos, evt. links til tidligere arbejde og et par ord om dig selv, herunder om evt. danseerfaring.

items.text:
**CALL FOR SOUND & LIGHTING BOARD Operators**

**Production:** *George Orwell‚Äôs 1984*
**Produced by:** PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS
**Location:** Three Stories Theater
937 Liberty Ave, Downtown Pittsburgh
**Performances:** December 4‚Äì7, 2025
**Contact:** playboxpgh@gmail.com

**PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS** is seeking a **Sound Board Operator** and a **Lighting Board Operator** for our upcoming production of *1984* by George Orwell, directed by M.A.C. This is a new concept for this story, completely Americanized through costumes, set design, sound, and overall aesthetic.

Our **full cast and crew of over 30 people** have already been hard at work bringing this show to life over the past few months. We have a complete design and stage management team in place; we are now looking for skilled operators to help us execute this ambitious and timely production during tech week and performances.

**POSITION DETAILS**
**Titles:** Sound Board Operator and Lighting Board Operator
**Compensation Type:** Volunteer / Possible post-show stipend
*(We want to be transparent: this is a volunteer position, but if funds allow, a small stipend may be available after the production.)*

**Dates & Commitment:**
* **Rehearsals (all optional for operators):** Sundays, 6‚Äì9 PM starting August 3, 2025
Trust Arts Education Center ‚Äî 807 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA
* **Tech Week:** November 24 ‚Äì December 3, 2025 (dark day on Thanksgiving) ‚Äî 937 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA
* **Performances:** December 4‚Äì7, 2025 (5 performances total)
Three Stories Theater ‚Äî 937 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA

We‚Äôre happy to work with your schedule. Please include any known conflicts when reaching out.

**QUALIFICATIONS**
* For Sound: Experience with QLab or a similar playback system
* For Lighting: Familiarity with ETC lighting consoles preferred
* Reliable, communicative, and calm under pressure
* Comfortable collaborating with an awesome stage management and design team! 

**TO APPLY**
Please email **playboxpgh@gmail.com** with:
* Resume (or a brief summary of your relevant experience) **This is super important, since we are using a Pittsburgh Cultural Trust space. They require a review of your resume to let you use the theatre tech equipment.*
* Availability during tech week and performances

If interested, we‚Äôll be in touch right away to discuss next steps.

Thank you!

Marc Palombo
PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS
